&lt;li&gt;Good at model based developing and C language for embedded coder&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiar with SOC, SOH, SOE, SOF, insulation detection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AutoSar , ISO26262 experience is much preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good English ability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
