&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provided technical support for production, formulated standard operation instructions for each process, and solved technical problems in the production process&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In-depth technical exchanges on the production site, providing guidance for key parts and processes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bachelor’s degree, major in mechatronics, electronics, electrical, process design&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At least 2 years working experience in PACK assembly or lithium battery industry&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good at analyzing and solving problems, have good communication and coordination skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Familiar with IATF16949 quality management system&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proficient in Office, AUTOCAD and other software&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have a certain ability to work under pressure, have a strong sense of team spirit and cooperation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
