&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Put forward the process optimization plan, carried out verification and result analysis, and completed the formulation, implementation and update of process documents&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsible for the analysis and defect improvement of adverse problems in the battery production process, identification of possible failure modes in the mass production process of new product introduction, and output effective process control methods&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsible for product process route and data collection and maintenance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsible for process optimization, improvement of process flow and parameters, and improvement of optimal rate&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
