&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bachelor’s degree or above, major in material, chemistry, mechanical science and engineering&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;More than 3 years of experience in lithium battery technology or product development&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Familiar with the manufacturing process standards of lithium batteries&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good team communication skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
