&lt;p&gt;Fully responsible for the quality of the project life cycle, ensure that the project research and development process is under control, promote the analysis and solution of the trial-production, experimental quality problems and after-sales problems of each project&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Summary of project quality experience&lt;/p&gt;
