&lt;p&gt;Bachelor’s degree or above, CET-4 or above, good English communication and coordination skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;More than 2 years of battery research and development projects, quality management and process management; At least 1 year R&amp;amp;D project management experience in related industry&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have the ability of quality system review and on-site audit, and can independently issue audit report&lt;/p&gt;
