&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong communication skills, organization and coordination skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Familiar with quality management system, quality management process and common quality management tools and analysis methods&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
