&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Confirm and run the company&#39;s quality objectives, effectively analyze the operation of the quality indicators of each department and organize the annual management review to ensure that the annual KPI indicators of the department are achieved and continuously improved&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsible for the company&#39;s quality control and quality standards related policies, processes, systems and operating norms of the formulation, inspection, implementation and improvement&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsible for quality team building, optimize the organizational structure of the department, clarify the responsibilities, powers, and obligations of each position, and allocate the appropriate personnel to build an efficient quality team&lt;/p&gt;
