&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Organize and coordinate the internal, customer and third-party to conduct system audit, process audit, product audit, hierarchical audit and other quality review work and track the resolution of the problem&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage daily quality work including laboratory and measurement management, supplier quality issues, advance quality planning, daily quality control, non-conforming product management and so on&lt;/p&gt;
