&lt;p&gt;Responsible for maintaining and communicating with the customer&#39;s corresponding department in quality management, ensuring that the quality of the company&#39;s products and services meets customer requirements, leading and passing customer audits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
