&lt;p&gt;Responsible for the company&#39;s various quality accident investigation, analysis, and proposed solutions.&amp;nbsp; For the major quality issues customers complain, recurring issues, shall guide, track and monitor progress of problem&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
