&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree or above (Chemical Engineering, Mechanical, Manufacturing preferred)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;More than 5 years of senior management experience in lithium battery industry, familiar with industry knowledge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good experience in quality management, excellent Engineering background, excellent thinking logic and coordination ability&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proficient in IATF-16949, ISO-14001, VDA6.3, Six Sigma, Lean Manufacturing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fluent spoken and written English.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Sales Manager (Drones Business Unit)&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SES AI Corp. (NYSE: SES) is dedicated to &lt;strong&gt;accelerating the world’s energy transition&lt;/strong&gt; through groundbreaking material discovery and advanced battery management. We are at the forefront of revolutionizing battery creation, pioneering the integration of &lt;strong&gt;cutting-edge machine learning&lt;/strong&gt; into our research and development. Our AI-enhanced, high-energy-density and high-power-density Li-Metal and Li-ion batteries are unique; they are the &lt;strong&gt;first in the world&lt;/strong&gt; to utilize electrolyte materials discovered by AI. This powerful combination of &quot;AI for science&quot; and material engineering enables batteries that can be used across various applications, including &lt;strong&gt;transportation (land and air), energy storage, robotics, and drones&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To learn more about us, please visit: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ses.ai&quot;&gt;www.ses.ai&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A highly competitive salary and robust benefits package, including comprehensive health coverage and an attractive equity/stock options program within our NYSE-listed company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to contribute directly to a meaningful scientific project—accelerating the global energy transition—with a clear and broad public impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in a dynamic, collaborative, and innovative environment at the intersection of AI and material science, driving the next generation of battery technology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Significant opportunities for professional growth and career development as you work alongside leading experts in AI, R&amp;amp;D, and engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to state-of-the-art facilities and proprietary technologies are used to discover and deploy AI-enhanced battery solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we Need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The SES AI Drones Business Unit team is seeking a motivated and technically minded Sales Manager. This is an entry-level position ideal for someone who is passionate about technology, marketing, and customer engagement. In this role, you will focus on&lt;strong&gt; selling our AI-enhanced battery cells for drones, robotics, and other applications.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/strong&gt;You will be identifying and targeting customers, managing accounts, and engaging with customers in the defense and commercial sectors at global trade shows and conferences. You will help communicate SES AI’s unique value proposition, bridging the gap between technology and practical applications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Duties and Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop an understanding of SES AI’s battery portfolio and related technology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and qualify new leads, set up discovery calls, and develop leads into opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nurture new opportunities and develop these into customers. Work with Drones BU Sales leadership to close opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meet and exceed sales performance goals and company-wide business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage sales accounts internally and external communication with the customers and key stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute outreach campaigns, content, and marketing initiatives to raise awareness of SES AI’s battery products in the battery and defense/

